@startuml
title Rappels et Notifications Email/SMS Reservations - Architecture logique

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Reservations" {
  [Reservation Source]
  [My Reservations UI]
}

package "Rappels" {
  [Reservation Event Adapter]
  [Event Recipient Router]
  [Hourly Reminder Scheduler]
  [Notification Composer]
  [Channel Selector]
}

package "Notifications" {
  [Delivery Gateway]
  [SMS Provider Adapter (Brevo)]
  [reservation_reminder_log]
  [gvv_error]
}

package "Administration" {
  [Admin Configuration]
  [User Reminder Preferences]
}

package "Triggers" {
  [Cron Trigger]
  [Public URL Trigger]
}

[Admin Configuration] --> [Hourly Reminder Scheduler] : activation section
[Cron Trigger] --> [Hourly Reminder Scheduler] : lancement horaire
[Public URL Trigger] --> [Hourly Reminder Scheduler] : lancement URL + secret
[Reservation Source] --> [Reservation Event Adapter] : event create|update|cancel
[My Reservations UI] --> [Reservation Source] : list user reservations\ndelete reservation\nopen add reservation
[My Reservations UI] --> [User Reminder Preferences] : channel + reminder period
[User Reminder Preferences] --> [Hourly Reminder Scheduler] : user period settings
[Reservation Event Adapter] --> [Event Recipient Router] : event create|update|cancel
[Event Recipient Router] --> [Notification Composer] : event_notification
[Event Recipient Router] --> [Notification Composer] : creator in crew -> notify second member
[Event Recipient Router] --> [Notification Composer] : creator third-party -> notify both crew
[Hourly Reminder Scheduler] --> [Reservation Source] : reservations existantes\n< 48h (jour meme inclus)
[Hourly Reminder Scheduler] --> [User Reminder Preferences] : read channel + period
[Hourly Reminder Scheduler] --> [Notification Composer] : scheduled_reminder
[Notification Composer] --> [Channel Selector] : canal=email|sms|email+sms

[Channel Selector] --> [Delivery Gateway] : envoi email
[Channel Selector] --> [SMS Provider Adapter (Brevo)] : envoi sms
[Delivery Gateway] --> [reservation_reminder_log] : unique_key + sent_at + message\nsource=event_*|cron|public_url\ntype=scheduled_reminder|event_notification\nstatus
[SMS Provider Adapter (Brevo)] --> [reservation_reminder_log] : unique_key + sent_at + message\nsource=event_*|cron|public_url\ntype=scheduled_reminder|event_notification\nstatus
[Delivery Gateway] --> [gvv_error] : on send failure only\nno automatic retry
[SMS Provider Adapter (Brevo)] --> [gvv_error] : on send failure only\nno automatic retry
[Hourly Reminder Scheduler] --> [reservation_reminder_log] : trace scheduler reminders
[Reservation Event Adapter] --> [reservation_reminder_log] : trace event intake

@enduml
